  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/a65cdb0d8406becc4a885a150659c936.poster.avif?t=1702461252\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/a65cdb0d8406becc4a885a150659c936.webm?t=1702461252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/a65cdb0d8406becc4a885a150659c936.mp4?t=1702461252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore a world enhanced by extreme view distance and lush visuals created with Unreal engine and new voxel technology.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Destroy</h2>Play with full destruction physics using a custom system created with multiplayer in mind.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/bc21e773c5566153630f9df562b70737.poster.avif?t=1702461252\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/bc21e773c5566153630f9df562b70737.webm?t=1702461252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/bc21e773c5566153630f9df562b70737.mp4?t=1702461252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight</h2>Loot weapons, cast spells, and fight animals and characters to survive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/ace09b9f5c9955469db9f930d16bc8da.poster.avif?t=1702461252\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/ace09b9f5c9955469db9f930d16bc8da.webm?t=1702461252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/ace09b9f5c9955469db9f930d16bc8da.mp4?t=1702461252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build</h2>Quickly plan with building tools, then recruit villagers to have them build.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/16f03c4c612c47158781957f38288ab4.poster.avif?t=1702461252\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/16f03c4c612c47158781957f38288ab4.webm?t=1702461252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/16f03c4c612c47158781957f38288ab4.mp4?t=1702461252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Attack and Defend</h2>Use siege weapons and magic to attack a friend's town or defend your own.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/49fd9e882ad99787c4eef0d5d498f2aa.poster.avif?t=1702461252\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/49fd9e882ad99787c4eef0d5d498f2aa.webm?t=1702461252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/49fd9e882ad99787c4eef0d5d498f2aa.mp4?t=1702461252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Craft and Trade</h2>Craft everything needed to start a town, then trade with your trader to buy crops to harvest. A Hunger system provides the need to eat as to not lose Max HP, but the option overeat to gain Max HP.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/99d3e87d822cd8d2e82236b3a1e0652d.avif?t=1702461252\" width=600 height=158 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Relax</h2>Get lost in a soundtrack of over two hours of sublime retro-inspired adventurous music, including 90 minutes by professional composer Claudia Correia.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1079300/extras/7d9ae0fb761b7e03de0ae4be3d101d57.avif?t=1702461252\" width=601 height=100 /></span>",
